<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/blog/">Blog</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Annual Physical</span>
  </div>
  <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Preventive Care · Dallas, TX</span>
  <h1 class="page-title fade-in">What an <em>annual physical</em><br>actually checks.</h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle fade-in">A walkthrough of every screening AymanCare performs during your yearly wellness visit in Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Valley Ranch — and why each one matters more than you might think.</p>
</section>
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 100px;">
  <div style="max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.8;">
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 01</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;"><em>Blood pressure</em> and cardiovascular health</h3>
      <p>High blood pressure affects 1 in 3 adults in the Dallas–Fort Worth area and causes no obvious symptoms — which is why it's called the silent killer. At every AymanCare visit we check it, but your annual physical is also the time to review your resting heart rate, listen to your heart and lungs, and assess your overall cardiovascular risk. For patients in East Dallas, Mid-Cities, Mesquite, and Irving, knowing your numbers is the first step toward protecting your long-term heart health.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 02</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;"><em>Blood work</em> — cholesterol, glucose, and more</h3>
      <p>A comprehensive metabolic panel reveals what no exam can see: cholesterol levels, blood glucose, kidney function, liver enzymes, and thyroid levels. Our on-site labs at all four Dallas-area AymanCare clinics process most routine bloodwork quickly. These numbers tell us if you're trending toward diabetes, heart disease, or thyroid dysfunction — conditions far easier to reverse early than to treat late.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 03</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;"><em>Cancer screenings</em> by age and risk</h3>
      <p>Depending on your age, sex, and family history, your annual physical at AymanCare triggers the right cancer screenings: colorectal screening starting at 45, breast cancer and cervical cancer screenings, lung cancer screening for smokers, and skin and prostate assessments. We serve patients across Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Valley Ranch and help you understand exactly which screenings apply to you and when.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 04</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;"><em>Immunizations</em> and booster review</h3>
      <p>Vaccines aren't just for children. Dallas-area adults need boosters for tetanus, shingles, pneumonia, flu, and COVID-19. At your AymanCare annual physical in Dallas TX or any of our DFW locations, we review your immunization record and make sure you're protected — especially important if you're over 50, immunocompromised, or caring for young children or elderly family members.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="l">◆ 05</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2;">Mental health and <em>lifestyle conversation</em></h3>
      <p>Your annual physical in Dallas isn't just labs and vitals. Our board-certified physicians take time to discuss sleep quality, stress levels, physical activity, diet, and mental health. Depression and anxiety screening are part of a complete wellness exam at AymanCare. These conversations often uncover the most important adjustments — ones no blood panel can detect. This level of care is available at every one of our four DFW locations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="neighborhood-band fade-in" style="margin-top: 60px;">
      <div>
        <span class="overline" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;">✦ Covered by most insurance</span>
        <h2>Annual physicals in <em>Dallas, TX</em> — often at no cost.</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Most insurance plans cover annual wellness exams at no cost to you. AymanCare accepts Medicare, Tricare, Aetna, BlueCross, Cigna, UnitedHealth, Humana, and more. Serving Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Valley Ranch (Irving).</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent">Book appointment →</a>
          <a href="/services/primary-care/" class="btn btn-ghost">Learn about primary care ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
